{"tid":523791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[窮人生仔正仆街] 其實生育真係應該規範化","createTime":"2018-01-09T02:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T12:07:34.000Z","uid":69810,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"208936dac89b94b8b0b890a6bb919425598824af","tid":523791,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"今次虐兒，上次道友媽肢解個女，次次出事都係幾類人<br />\n1. 新移民<br />\n2. 讀唔成書好細個就生仔嘅MK<br />\n呢啲人生仔永遠唔會好好教育，就算唔出事大家都會知道佢地命途唔會好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真生仔其實真係唔係人權咁簡單，有咩事成為社會負擔都係大家交稅搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得生育前應該要進行一系列資產、學歷、品格審查，例如要戶口要有一定嘅錢，父母要有一定學歷先可以生，否則只會有更多類似悲劇出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同意窮人MK唔俾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同意，生仔係人權，人人都應該生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c72326d917f48f478dbdab83b776253611796ed","tid":523791,"uid":69810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但窮人唔生長遠邊有人掃街呢？"},{"pid":"b9f971f65982d13065b8ed16a6ac55f80baba04c","tid":523791,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c72326d917f48f478dbdab83b776253611796ed","tid":523791,"uid":69810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但窮人唔生長遠邊有人掃街呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"好似新加坡咁用外奴又得唔得？"},{"pid":"32543ddf2b5efed689ae21d5cfb195df074c3171","tid":523791,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <